{"tid":2322251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［唔好扮嘢］留得喺香港做公務員當然要簽啦，唔通仲諗住有食兩家茶飯？","createTime":"2020-12-12T07:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T07:45:23.000Z","uid":219007,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5748c8a8cbb7686c15f3dcfa164000669584031d","tid":2322251,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T07:31:43.000Z","msg":"而家喺中央全面管治，依家就係要歸邊。 你估仲可以好似以前咁乜都唔關我事，兩邊Lam盡着數? <br />\n<br />\n唔好再同我講乜嘢公務員係市民公僕乜乜大道理，依家講呢啲係嘥鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留喺香港既又唔肯屈服嘅人注定揸兜乞食，一個唔好彩就坐一世監，出到嚟乞食都冇份，因為popo連乞E都趕～<br />\n<br />\n一係你就移民，否則留得喺香港就係要投共先有飯食！呢個就係香港嘅現實環境！ 唔單止淨係公務員，好快各行各業都係自我審查㗎啦，到時個個都要簽，公司對你好啲最多就炒人，揸淨黎做就報國安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家有得走就好走啦，遲吓冇得你走就隨時後悔一世，兒子兒孫怨你一生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd64cea3fe9aae9ad44cca5868774cb9ba3ae4fc","tid":2322251,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T07:38:41.000Z","msg":"damn撚鳩true <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdca8fbbfb8ca1448b3a798721ebdf609326db30","tid":2322251,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T07:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5aec7596b9a94102a69b6aa0